hindi tinatablan ng makamundong alikabok♪

00:15:26.432 --> 00:15:32.576
♪Nakangiting mga tingin ay nagsusulat ng kawalang-hanggan♪

00:16:24.200 --> 00:16:26.160
(Ang pag-ibig ay makasarili,)

00:16:26.920 --> 00:16:29.280
(gayunpaman ang tunay na debosyon ay hindi makasarili.)

00:16:30.120 --> 00:16:32.960
(Makasarili kayo
sa isa't isa.)

00:16:33.280 --> 00:16:36.000
(Samantala, kayong dalawa
ay walang pag-iimbot na bumitaw sa isa't isa.)

00:16:36.200 --> 00:16:38.360
(Itong kabalintunaan na gusot)

00:16:38.480 --> 00:16:40.400
(ang iyong tunay na kapalaran.)

00:16:41.280 --> 00:16:42.480
(pagkabulag ni Zixuan)

00:16:42.920 --> 00:16:44.280
(simula pa lang.)

00:16:45.080 --> 00:16:46.680
(Sinaway niya ang kanyang kapalaran)

00:16:46.840 --> 00:16:48.560
(at makasarili kang pinanatili sa tabi niya.)

00:16:48.960 --> 00:16:51.200
(Mawawala siya sa wakas.)

00:16:51.520 --> 00:16:52.720
(Upang iligtas siya,)

00:16:53.120 --> 00:16:54.640
(kailangan mong umalis,)

00:16:55.120 --> 00:16:57.840
(walang pag-iimbot na binitawan siya.)

00:16:58.600 --> 00:16:59.400
(Pagkatapos,)

00:16:59.720 --> 00:17:02.400
(lahat ng alaala
sa pagitan mo at ni Zixuan ay maglalaho.)

00:17:02.560 --> 00:17:05.320
(Ang oras ay magbabalik
sa gabi ng iyong kasal.)

00:17:06.440 --> 00:17:08.920
(Kakalimutan niya lahat ng tungkol sayo)

00:17:09.480 --> 00:17:11.440
(at pakasalan ang orihinal na Wei Xiaotang,)

00:17:12.240 --> 00:17:14.200
(namumuhay ng maligaya magpakailanman.)

00:17:16.224 --> 00:17:21.024
(Li's Tea Estate)

00:17:43.520 --> 00:17:44.320
Zixuan.

00:17:45.080 --> 00:17:47.000
Lumalamig na ang panahon.

00:17:47.400 --> 00:17:48.680
Kaya inutusan ko ang mga katulong

00:17:48.680 --> 00:17:50.200
para gumawa ka pa ng damit.

00:17:50.920 --> 00:17:52.440
Kapag handa na sila,

00:17:52.880 --> 00:17:54.800
maaari mong subukan ang mga ito.

00:17:55.680 --> 00:17:56.160
Sige.

00:18:00.640 --> 00:18:03.120
Mga bagong pritong cake!

00:18:05.280 --> 00:18:06.080
anong mali?

00:18:07.720 --> 00:18:09.520
Sir, gusto mo ng fried cake?

00:18:34.080 --> 00:18:34.880
Zixuan.

00:18:35.520 --> 00:18:37.440
Street food ito.

00:18:37.440 --> 00:18:38.560
Hindi pa namin nasubukan.

00:18:39.200 --> 00:18:40.880
Sino ang nakakaalam kung ito ay malinis?

00:18:44.480 --> 00:18:45.480
kahit papaano,

00:18:46.120 --> 00:18:47.840
itong piniritong cake

00:18:48.240 --> 00:18:49.240
pamilyar ang amoy.

00:18:50.560 --> 00:18:51.920
As if I share this

00:18:52.360 --> 00:18:53.360
may kasama kanina.

00:18:57.200 --> 00:18:57.920
Pero hindi ko mahanap

00:18:59.800 --> 00:19:00.600
yung taong yun ulit.

00:19:15.200 --> 00:19:16.320
(Li Zixuan.)

00:19:49.984 --> 00:19:56.448
(Ang Katapusan)

00:19:56.448 --> 00:19:58.336
(Ipagpapatuloy...)

